- **Blocking gap: encryption format does not match the “unreadable binary” done condition.** `save_license_key()` XORs then Base64-encodes (`_encrypt_key`) before writing. Base64 produces plain ASCII text, so `.license_key` is still text-readable (though obfuscated), not binary-looking ciphertext as requested.
